texts.content: <outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[现在 如果还想着“通过艺考低分进高校”]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[可能就行不通了]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[前些日子教育部发布《关于做好2023年普通]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[高等学校部分特殊类型招生工作的通知》]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[通知提出艺术类本科专业高考文化课]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[录取控制分数线 原则上不低于二本线的75%]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[舞蹈学类 表演等专业可适当降低要求]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[适度提高艺术学理论类 戏剧与影视学类等有关]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[本科专业的文化课录取线]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[这也意味着接下来艺术类专业文化课]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[分数线将逐步提高]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[有不少艺考生在准备艺考期间终止]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[了文化课的学习 全力以赴准备专业课]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[而普通考生在这段时间进行了大量的基础复习]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[占尽先机]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[艺考生在专业课考试结束后该如何摆脱不利形势]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[冲刺文化课?]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[找准自己的定位]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[在开始复习之前]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[要对自己的学习状况有一个充分的了解]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[只有这样才能做好更适合自己的学习计划]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[从过去的数据来看]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[有些同学复习期间没有很好的效果]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[背后的原因并不是不够努力]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[而是没有明确自己的定位]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[复习时切忌盲目跟从 要找准自己的节奏]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[用适合自己的学习方法]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[在查找自己的问题时可以利用下面几个办法:]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[1了解自己当前的学习水平]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[确定目前成绩和目标成绩的差距]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[2 将差距分布给不同学科 确定各学科的差距]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[3 继续拆解每个学科各个知识点的掌握情况]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[4 针对各个知识点的掌握情况制定]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[自己的学习计划]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[抓牢基础知识]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[即使艺考生文化课的分数线增长已成为趋势]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[但分数线仍会比普通考生低一些]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[所以最关键的是掌握好基础知识]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[复习期间就要紧跟老师的思路]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[集中总结老师提到的基础重点]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[如果遇到不明白的问题及时解决]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[另外要懂得总结学习规律]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[然后自己针对漏缺的知识点加强练习]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[及时调整心态]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[很多艺考生在刚开始复习文化课时会一头雾水]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[在发现自己有些知识点掌握得不太好后很容易]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[丧失学习文化课的信心]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[遇到不会的问题可以问老师 一定要调整好心态]</font></color></size></outline>

<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[家里有条件的话也可以选择针对艺考生开放]</font></color></size></outline>
<outline color=(1,1,1,1) width=0.08><size=11><color=(0,0,0,1)><font id="" path="D:/MyTools/JianyingPro/3.4.1.9179/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf">[的文化课培训班]</font></color></size></outline>
